- Yeah.

40:26.875 --> 40:28.750
- Give me a hug.
That was incredible.

40:28.750 --> 40:30.458
We're all done.

40:30.458 --> 40:33.458
- I couldn't have done
it without you, honestly.

40:33.458 --> 40:36.917
- This--I'm just really upset.

