- She's not happy.

41:25.792 --> 41:28.125
- Listen...
- Just chill. It's all good.

41:28.125 --> 41:29.750
- You're not the chef
on this boat.

41:29.750 --> 41:31.250
There's no reason
you should feel bad

41:31.250 --> 41:33.250
about anything
that happened this evening.

41:33.250 --> 41:35.292
You're a hard worker.
You have a positive attitude.

41:35.292 --> 41:38.083
- You dealt with a very
stressful situation tonight.

41:38.083 --> 41:40.167
It was 12 courses.

