41:50.000 --> 41:52.042
I was stressed out about it.

41:52.042 --> 41:56.333
Now it's like, if I shout
at someone it's like "Oh, God."

41:56.333 --> 42:00.208
- I can't deal with this.
It's so f---ed up.

42:07.375 --> 42:12.208
- If you're sensitive,
stay out of the f---ing kitchen.

42:12.208 --> 42:15.542
- I'm over it.

42:20.208 --> 42:23.625
- Try and just get through
the next few days.

42:23.625 --> 42:27.500
- This negative energy, like,
this is not for me.

42:31.750 --> 42:33.250
- Next on "Below Deck"...

42:33.250 --> 42:35.500
- Sierra, she, like,
