42:37.000 --> 42:38.542
- I don't want her
to become discouraged.

42:38.542 --> 42:40.750
- Absolutely.
- I can't wait to come home.

42:40.750 --> 42:42.417
- We will be getting
our new deckhand.

42:42.417 --> 42:44.042
- For this shadow?
- Yep, he's pretty green.

42:44.042 --> 42:45.583
- Oh, f---.

